reviews.customers_say: Customers find the cardigan soft and comfortable, with a nice pattern and great colors. The sweater is lightweight, fits as expected, and is warm, with one customer noting it's perfect for cooler winter weather. They appreciate its quality, with one describing it as a wonderful layering piece.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice sweater
items.body: Very cute and colorful. Fits true to size. It is soft and comfortable and fairly priced. Read more
items.author: RB

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Soft, warm, beautiful winter sweater!
items.body: This is a soft beautiful winter sweater. It's my 2nd YesNo brand sweater purchase and I absolutely love it! It's very high quality and fits as expected. If you're looking for a pretty winter sweater, this is absolutely worth every penny! Highly recommended! Read more
items.author: J.Adams

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars LOVE this ...
items.body: Soooo soft, warm and not heavy, a design to make you smile, and great quality all around ...even arrived with extra buttons. I have a couple of these that are the same material, different print designs and are overhead, so I decided to purchase a cardigan. Very pleased with this purchase! Read more
items.author: Ducks

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Runs large
items.body: Runs large. Nice color and the texture is super soft Read more
items.author: Andria Cooke

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Soft and warm!
items.body: Soft and warm, I love this sweater. Design is a heat transfer. So far I've worn brown, teal, yellow, and gold t-shirts under it. Good length and light weight. Pattern is distinctive and I've received many compliments. Read more
items.author: Daffodilynn

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Smaller than expected for an "oversized Large".
items.body: I have purchased two of these sweaters before and love them. They are soft, comfortable and the graphics are colorful and beautiful. As usual I purchased a Large I was disappointed to see that it ran smaller than the other sweaters. It fits but the sleeves are shorter and the roominest that I loved in the others is not there. I debated on returning it for a larger size but will gift it to my daughter instead. Read more
items.author: jh

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality
items.body: Very soft thin but warm, beautiful colors Read more
items.author: Linda Dominguez

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Fabric feels great.
items.body: The photos are beautiful! However the print is stamped on not woven into the fabric as it looks in the photo. The fabric is warm and feels amazing. Read more
items.author: Belinda King

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

For the best look, smooth the fabric, check the neckline placement, and pair it with shoes that match the occasion and the hem length.

Comfort comes from both the cut and the fabric, so selecting your preferred fit makes a noticeable difference over a full day of wear.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Floral 186, Floral 163, Floral 01, Floral 101, Floral 111, Floral 110, Floral 121, Floral 106, Floral 108, Floral 119. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
